      <li><font color="#009000"><strong> <a href="http://news.zdnet.co.uk/story/0,,t269-s2134164,00.html?rtag=zdnetukhompage"> 
        OpenBSD releases version 3.3</a>, ZDNet UK. </strong></font> </li>
      <li><font color="#009000"><strong> <a href="http://www.net-security.org/article.php?id=480"> 
        OpenBSD 3.3 has been released</a>, Help Net Security, Croatia. </strong></font> 
      </li>
