<h2>Décembre 2000</h2>
<ul>
  <li><font color="#009000"><strong> <a href="http://eltoday.com/article.php3?ltsn=2000-12-26-001-13-PS">Florist.com Blossoms 
    with Open Source E-Commerce Software from Akopia</a>, Enterprise Linux Today, 
